---
// AboutB.astro - Card-based Layout Design
---

<section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-pink-light">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
    <!-- Header Section -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-title text-brown mb-6">
        ELLA SKIN & SPA WELLNESS
      </h1>
      <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-brown mx-auto"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Content Grid -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      
      <!-- Mission Card -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg border border-pink/20 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-2">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-brown to-brown-light rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-title text-brown mb-4 text-center">Nuestra Misión</h3>
        <p class="text-black font-sans leading-relaxed">
          En ELLA SKIN & SPA WELLNESS, misión es guiarte hacia el bienestar integral y la belleza.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Technology Card -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg border border-pink/20 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-2">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-pink to-pink-light rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-title text-brown mb-4 text-center">Tecnología Avanzada</h3>
        <p class="text-black font-sans leading-relaxed">
          He creado un espacio donde la tecnología de vanguardia y la calidez humana se fusionan para ofrecerte una experiencia de spa única y personalizada.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Team Card -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg border border-pink/20 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-2">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-brown-light to-brown rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197m13.5-9a2.5 2.5 0 11-5 0 2.5 2.5 0 015 0z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-title text-brown mb-4 text-center">Equipo Especializado</h3>
        <p class="text-black font-sans leading-relaxed">
          Cuento con un equipo de especialistas apasionados que se dedican a salud y belleza, utilizando productos de alta calidad y técnicas avanzadas.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Wellness Card -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg border border-pink/20 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-2 md:col-span-2 lg:col-span-1">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-pink-light to-pink rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-title text-brown mb-4 text-center">Tu Bienestar</h3>
        <p class="text-black font-sans leading-relaxed">
          Descubre un lugar para desconectar y reconectar contigo mismo. En ELLA SKIN & SPA WELLNESS, bienestar es mi prioridad.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Experience Card -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-brown to-brown-light rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg text-white md:col-span-2 lg:col-span-2">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-white/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-6">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 3v4M3 5h4M6 17v4m-2-2h4m5-16l2.286 6.857L21 12l-5.714 2.143L13 21l-2.286-6.857L5 12l5.714-2.143L13 3z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-3xl font-title">Experiencia Única</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-lg font-sans leading-relaxed opacity-90">
          Cada visita a ELLA SKIN & SPA WELLNESS es una experiencia personalizada diseñada para tu bienestar integral. 
          Nuestro compromiso es brindarte el cuidado que mereces en un ambiente de tranquilidad y excelencia.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section> 